quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  54,9,"Ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe nuuhu …ìen yedduno. ∆Åe fenni jeyaa…óo Amen on, …ìe wi'i : \"Ko jinnaa…óo!\", o kammbanaa"
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Min on ko mi foolaa…óo, faabo [lam]"
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbu…óe kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam"
  54,12,Men fuccitiri leydi ndin …ìulli. Ndiye …óen fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde
  54,13,"Men roondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e pe≈ãe"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka Amen. ∆äum ko njo…ìdi [Nuuhu] fennanoo…óo on. @Corrected"
  54,15,"Gom…óii Men accirii [kon ko Men wa…ói …ìe] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi waajitoray…óo"
  54,16,Taskii ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,17,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,18,Aadi'en fennuno. Taskee ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,19,"Men wurtu e ma…ì…ìe henndu sattundu, e √±alaande hiitaande, duumiinde"
  54,20,"hindu wippitira yim…ìe …ìen, wa si tawii ko …ìe da∆¥∆¥e tamaro irtaa…óe"
  54,21,Taskee ko honno lepte Am …óen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,22,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,23,Samuuda'en fennuno waaju ngun
  54,24,"…ìe wi'i: \"Kere ko ne…ó…óo gooto e amen woni ko men jokkata? Haray men wonii ontuma e nder majjere e tamperere"
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jantoore nden werlaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko fenoowo nii, townitii…óo"
  54,26,"Aray …ìe annda (√ëalnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni fenoowo townitii…óo on"
  54,27,"Ko Men wurtiroo…ìe ngelooba ndewa mbam, jarribagol …ìe. Aynitu …ìe, mu√±√±o…óaa"
  54,28,"Humpitu …ìe wonnde ndiyam …óam ko sennndaa…óam hakkunde ma…ì…ìe [e ngelooba mbam]; kala yaray ge…ìal mun"
  54,29,"∆Åe noddi wonndii…óo ma…ì…ìe, o jonni [kaafa kan], o sodi [mba]"
  54,30,Teskii ko honno lepte Am …óen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,31,"Ko haacaango wooturu tun Men wurti e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wa'i wa ledde yooru…óe muncaa…óe"
  54,32,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,33,Yim…ìe Luutu …ìen fennuno jertine …óen
  54,34,"Men wurtuno henndu kaa∆¥e e ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa e …ìeynguure Luutu nden, Men da…óndirno …ìen ka wenndo"
  54,35,"mo∆¥∆¥ere immorde e Amen. Ko non Men yo…ìitirta kala yettu…óo [neema Allah on]"
  54,36,Gom…óii le o jertinirno …ìe nanngal Amen cattungal ngal. Kono …ìe sikkitii jertinol ngol
  54,37,"Gom…óii …ìe …óa…ì…ìirno mo [bonidugol e ho…ó…ìe makko …ìen]. Men mehi gite ma…ì…ìe …óen. \"Mee…óee lepte …óen e jertinol Am ngol"
  54,38,"Gom…óii ko bimmbi law, woni ko lepte duumii…óe dawirani …ìe"
  54,39,Mee…óee lepte e jertinol Am
  54,40,Gom…óii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitor…óo
  54,41,Gom…óii jertinaango ngon arii e yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen
  54,42,"∆Åe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen fow. Men nanngiri …ìe, nanngal Foolu…óo Hattan…óo"
  54,43,Kere ko heefer…ìe mon …ìen …ìuri …ìeya mo∆¥∆¥ude? Kaa ko da…óugol woodani on ka ∆äeri
  54,44,"Kaa hara …ìe wi'ay : \"Menen ko men dental wallindiroo…ìe"
  54,45,"Aray nde dental [ma…ì…ìe] ngal foolee, …ìe runntina …ìabbe ma…ì…ìe"
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darngal ngal woni kammbaa ma…ì…ìe on, Ko Darngal non …ìuri mawnude e haa…óude"
  54,47,"Pellet, bom…ìe …ìen wonii e majjere e ooyunge"
  54,48,"√ëalnde …ìe daasiroytee geece ma…ì…ìe …óen ka nder Yiite, (…ìe wi'anee): \"Mee…óee meemugol Saqara"
  54,49,Menen Men tagir huunde kala e e…ì…ìoore
  54,50,"Yamiroore Amen wonaali, si wanaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hin∆¥aango yiitere"
  54,51,Gom…óii Men halkiino yeradii…ìe mon. Hara wooday waajitoray…óo
  54,52,Kala huunde nde …ìe golli no ka nder …óeri
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko winndaa…óum"
  54,54,"Pellet, gom…óu…ìe …ìen wonii e Aljannaaji e can…ói"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka Laam…óo Hattan…óo"